Class PayRoll

java.lang.Object
  PayRoll

public class PayRoll
extends java.lang.Object

payRoll class contains a varying usage of methods to create a list of employee Objects and read them in from a text file, from printing the full information of the employees to printing just their first and last names or finding speific employee information contained in the list by operating the ObjectList class.

Version:
Final version 4/27/2018
Author:
Eric Davey
